OL,3,COverpaying for overcrowding? Almost a
OL,4,Cquarter of train users have to stand
OL,6,FRail services are getting more and
OL,7,Fmore overcrowded as passenger numbers
OL,8,Frebound to pre-pandemic levels, ITV
OL,9,FNews Consumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,11,FWords by Daniel Boal, ITV News Producer
OL,13,FNearly a quarter of train passengers
OL,14,Fin England and Wales are unable to sit
OL,15,Fdown on services due to overcrowding,
OL,16,Faccording to new figures.
