OL,3,COverpaying for overcrowding? Almost a
OL,4,Cquarter of train users have to stand
OL,6,FThey also suggested that overcrowding
OL,7,Fis largely a symptom of rail
OL,8,Fcancellations.
OL,10,FAlex Robertson, chief executive of
OL,11,FTransport Focus said: "We asked people
OL,12,Fwhat their priorities are when it
OL,13,Fcomes to catching a train, and top
OL,14,Ffive was getting a seat.
OL,16,F"We have seen demand go up in the last
OL,17,Fyear. What we really need to do is get
OL,18,Fthose cancellations down. That's the
OL,19,Fabsolute number one thing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
