OL,6,F"Let's get a regular service so you're
OL,7,Fnot having a service cancel and then
OL,8,Fyou're getting more people on the next
OL,9,Ftrain. And that's been static for the
OL,10,Flast year. A couple of years,
OL,11,Factually. If you look back 15 years
OL,12,Fago, we had cancellations about half
OL,13,Fthe way of now. So there's a big focus
OL,14,Fon getting that down."
OL,16,FOn a typical day in autumn 2024, the
OL,17,Fcity with the highest number of daily
OL,18,Fpassenger arrivals was London, with an
OL,19,Faverage of 1,207,600 passenger
OL,20,Farrivals.
