OL,11,FHe said: "The most important thing is
OL,12,Fletting people know, as far in advance
OL,13,Fas possible, what trains are running
OL,14,Fand where there might be risks.
OL,16,F"So people can adjust their travel
OL,17,Fplans. If they know there's going to
OL,18,Fbe crowding, there's going to be
OL,19,Fproblems on a particular day.
